Class DisplayTextBoxesCAE

  • java.lang.Object
    • etomica.graphics.Display
      • etomica.graphics.DisplayTextBoxesCAE
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDataSink, GraphicalElement

    public class DisplayTextBoxesCAE
extends Display
implements IDataSink
    Display that presents three boxes with the current value, average, and error, respectively, given by an AccumulatorAverage.

        Returns a DataProcessor that casts the data that will be given to this DataSink to a form that it can accept. Returns null if the Data is acceptable without casting. Otherwise object that is pushing the Data into this DataSink is responsible for filtering the Data through the returned DataTransformer.
